---
import LandingPage from '../../layouts/LandingPage.astro';
---
<LandingPage 
  title="Immersive 3D Live Tracking" 
  description="Experience port traffic like never before. Dive into a cinematic, real-time 3D environment powered by actual port photogrammetry and live telemetry."
>
  <div class="feature-block">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Cinematic Drone Autopilot</h2>
      <p>Engage the autopilot to take a breathtaking, low-altitude tour of your port. The camera automatically swoops between the most active and largest vessels, providing a stunning overview for operation centers or public displays.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">🚁</div>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-block reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Real-Time Environment Sync</h2>
      <p>The 3D world mirrors reality perfectly. Dynamic particle wakes trail behind fast-moving vessels, while the sun and shadows are synchronized with the exact time of day in your port.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">🌅</div>
  </div>
</LandingPage>
